      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new streetwear line and i really want to capture that \"authentic urban\" vibe without it looking like total cultural appropriation. can u help me break down what the core aesthetic of urban culture is right now? like, what elements make it feel real and not just some corporate version?",
