      "content": "that makes sense. but when u say \"cultural roots,\" who are we actually talking about? like, if i want this to feel \"street\" and authentic, what are the specific demographics or groups that define that aesthetic? i dont want to accidentally lean into something that doesn't fit the \"real\" urban look.",
